14 September 2011All media are invited to a press briefing at the conclusion of the African Ministerial Conference on Climate-Smart Agriculture.The media briefing will take place as follows: Date: 14 September 2011 Time: 15h00 Venue: Westcliff Hotel, Saxonwold, JohannesburgThe African Ministerial Conference is hosted by the Minister of Agriculture, Ms Tina Joemat-Pettersson with the support of the African Union (AU), United Nation Food and Agriculture Organization (FAO) and the World Bank.The conference is a build-up event towards the upcoming UN Climate Change Conference taking place in Durban 28 November to 9 December 2011.For accreditation purposes kindly send your name, ID/Passport number, media house and contact details to: Takalani Mashamba Cell: 078 252 3722 E-mail: Takalani@gcis.gov.zaIssued by: Government Communications (GCIS)